Package: system-docker-compose
Architecture: all
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Provides: system-docker-compose
Description: Run docker-compose at boot as part of systemd units
 Set the docker-compose file in /etc/docker-compose and it will be run
 as a systemd daemon. Containers will be automatically updated via the
 homonym systemd timer.

